channel.title: Object not spanwing :l
channel.description:
I'm trying to put 2 bank booth down, but no matter what I've done so far it just hasn't worked. I added the objects in client.java and in objects.cfg, but still nothing is there.
Code for Client.java: x y id face title makeGlobalObject (2736, 3476, 2213, -1, 10); // bank booth 1 - shops makeGlobalObject (2737, 3476, 2213, -1, 10); // bank booth 2 - shops
Code for Objects.cfg: id x y height face type open Object = 2213 2736 3476 0 -1 1 false Bank booth 1 - shops Object = 2213 2737 3476 0 -1 1 false Bank booth 2 - shops
What could I be doing wrong? I've tried all the codes for bank booth but nothing has worked. I am using a 317 blank source and client.
